    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  P-Ca-ion &gt; 1,30 mmol/l

          -  P-PTH &gt; 5 pmol/l

          -  P-OH25-vitamin D &lt; 80 nmol/l

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  P-creatinin &gt; 120 mumol/l

          -  usage of Etalpha, Mimpara

          -  Cancer

          -  Sarcoidosis

          -  malabsorption

          -  pancreatitis

          -  alcohol abuse

          -  pregnancy
      </textblock>
